{
  "id": "adv_event_2504_01_03",
  "title": "アリスオーデ\nィション",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The Next Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "演目は『不思議の国のアリス』で決まりとして\n肝心の配役なんやけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ the program is settled as Alice in Wonderland‚\nbut the important part is the casting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8666666667,
      "endTime": 8.0166665713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "当然、アリス役は私がやりますわ\n主役はスーパーアイドルの私以外あり得ませんわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Naturally‚ I’ll be playing Alice.\nThere’s no way anyone but a super idol like me could be the lead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.230000019,
      "endTime": 17.6555800437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "この劇団の座長は私……\nアリス役は私がやる……これは譲れない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m the leader of this troupe…\nI’ll play Alice… this is something I won’t give up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.7622470538,
      "endTime": 23.7822468439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "……さっきからずっとこんな調子で\n話が一向にまとまらへんなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…They’ve been like this the whole time‚\nand the discussion isn’t getting anywhere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9755800247,
      "endTime": 29.791997051099997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "すずはいつものことだけど\n雫がここまで強情を張るのはめずらしいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu being like this is normal‚\nbut it’s rare to see Shizuku this stubborn.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9986637751,
      "endTime": 35.9397522608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "「演劇をやりたい」って劇団★見を立ち上げたのは\n雫ちゃんだからね。それだけやる気に燃えてるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan was the one who said she wanted to do theater\nand founded Troupe★Hoshimi‚ after all. She’s just that fired up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1264189083,
      "endTime": 44.5629497845,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "話し合いで決めるのは難しそうやし……\nここは公平にオーディションしてみるのはどうやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks tough to decide this by discussion alone…\nHow about holding a fair audition instead?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7496165275,
      "endTime": 51.649616432100004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "二人にアリス役を演じてもろて\nうちら三人で審査して、誰にするか決めるんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll have both of you perform as Alice‚\nand the three of us will judge and decide who gets the role.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8362829844,
      "endTime": 58.8197522798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "より多くの票を集めた方がアリス役ですわね\n望むところですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoever gets more votes becomes Alice‚ right?\nThat’s exactly what I want!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0197521845,
      "endTime": 65.8029269853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "絶対に負けたくない……このオーディション……\nすずちゃんに勝って、アリスになるのは私……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I absolutely don’t want to lose… this audition…\nI’ll beat Suzu-chan and become Alice…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.0095937092,
      "endTime": 72.74517205549999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ほな、うちが原作のワンシーンを台本に書き起こすから\n三十分後にスタジオでオーディション開始や",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright then‚ I’ll adapt one scene from the original into a script‚\nand we’ll start the audition in the studio in thirty minutes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9518388748,
      "endTime": 80.5961019517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――三十分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Thirty Minutes Later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.5961017609,
      "endTime": 82.7361017943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "「あれは……うさぎが喋りながら走ってる……？」\nダメ……もっと大きな声で感情を込めて言わないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“That is… a rabbit running while talking…?”\nNo… I need to say it louder‚ with more emotion…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5961037954,
      "endTime": 93.92551415770001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10625.530815200009
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、もうすぐオーディションの時間やけど\n調子はどないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan‚ the audition’s about to start.\nHow are you feeling?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.138847224,
      "endTime": 99.9925662677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "調子は、良くない……大声を出すのは苦手で……\nセリフに感情を込めるのも、難しい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not great… I’m bad at raising my voice…\nAnd putting emotion into lines is hard…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1792329152,
      "endTime": 108.47668946569999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "セリフに気持ちを乗せるのって結構難しいんよね\nうちもそれで苦労したから、気持ちは分かります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Conveying emotion through lines is pretty hard‚ yeah.\nI struggled with that too‚ so I know how you feel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6766895611,
      "endTime": 117.0458051998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "「あれは！　うさぎが喋りながら走ってる！？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“That is! A rabbit running while talking!?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2524720191,
      "endTime": 121.7052840232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "向こうですずちゃんも練習してはるなぁ\nすずちゃんらしい、気持ちのこもった大きな声やわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like Suzu-chan’s practicing over there too.\nThat big‚ heartfelt voice is so like her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.8919507662,
      "endTime": 129.1364407221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "分かる……迷いがなくて、思い切りがいいから……\n聞いてて気持ちいい……あれは私には真似出来ない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know… there’s no hesitation‚ she commits fully…\nIt feels good just listening… I can’t imitate that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.3297738074,
      "endTime": 137.82015962600002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "……不思議やってんけど雫ちゃんはどうしてそこまで\n主役のアリスにこだわるん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’ve been wondering‚ but why are you so set\non playing Alice‚ the lead role?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0334926922,
      "endTime": 143.9026083308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "……最初は、好きなお話だからとか……私が座長だから\nとか……そういういろんな理由で立候補したけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…At first‚ it was because I love the story… because I’m the leader…\nI had all sorts of reasons when I put myself forward…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.1159414926,
      "endTime": 154.0659411111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "今、一番大きな理由は……\nすずちゃんに勝ちたいから……かな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But right now‚ the biggest reason is…\nbecause I want to beat Suzu-chan… maybe…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.2726076442,
      "endTime": 161.43260777769999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんは、今一番輝いてるアイドルの一人……\nそれは、ドルオタの私が誰よりもよく分かってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan is one of the brightest idols right now…\nAs an idol fan‚ I understand that better than anyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.6259409585,
      "endTime": 170.74594065329998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ、負けたくない……仲間として……\nアイドルの頂点を目指すライバルとして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s exactly why I don’t want to lose… as a teammate…\nand as a rival aiming for the top of the idol world…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.9326073962,
      "endTime": 179.5726075488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "成り行きで始まったオーディションだけど……\nすずちゃんとの真剣勝負……私は、勝ちたい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This audition started by chance‚ but…\nin this serious match with Suzu-chan… I want to win…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.7659406342,
      "endTime": 187.4224031128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "仲間でライバル。だから負けたくない……\nその気持ち、よう分かります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Teammates and rivals—that’s why you don’t want to lose…\nI really understand that feeling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.629069932,
      "endTime": 195.9890703515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "立場上、どっちかに肩入れは出来へんけど……\nオーディション、いい勝負が出来るとええね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t take sides because of my position‚ but…\nI hope it turns into a good‚ close match.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.1757369992,
      "endTime": 203.491564655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
